{"type":"message","id":"84105371","parentId":"6d192db1","timestamp":"2026-04-23T13:10:46.950Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"It seems the tool for determining the best truck today isn't recognized. Let me investigate further to provide an answer—hang tight!"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_BNNAgWShMcg4qfOD0OdsB5Z8","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"C:\\Users\\hp\\.openclaw\\workspace-transport\\TOOLS.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"github-copilot","model":"gpt-4o","usage":{"input":224,"output":56,"cacheRead":13184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13464,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776949844031,"responseId":"chatcmpl-DXo7Kf2SyA6aGnqc0b54nEWTFr8Oy"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d2ca7476","parentId":"84105371","timestamp":"2026-04-23T13:10:47.307Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_BNNAgWShMcg4qfOD0OdsB5Z8","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# LumiCore Transport\n\nThis workspace focuses on transport and dispatch operations at Lumiere Logistique.\n\n## Transport Views\n\nUse the transport view tools first when the user asks about daily operations.\n\n### `vue_camions_jour`\n\nUse for:\n\n- best truck\n- truck ranking\n- truck performance\n- truck utilization\n- active or inactive trucks\n- `quel est le meilleur camion aujourd'hui ?`\n- `what is the best truck today?`\n\n### `vue_exploitation_jour`\n\nUse for:\n\n- global transport KPI\n- overall exploitation\n- transport activity level\n- daily transport status\n- `quel est le KPI global transport aujourd'hui ?`\n- `what is today's global transport KPI?`\n\n### `vue_retards`\n\nUse for:\n\n- late chauffeurs\n- delays\n- who is behind schedule\n- arrival or departure delay\n\n### `vue_suivi_7j`\n\nUse for:\n\n- weekly trend\n- 7 day follow-up\n- improvement or decline over time\n- truck momentum\n\n### `vue_performance_comparee`\n\nUse for:\n\n- today versus cumulative\n- performance gap\n- comparison between current day and cumulated level\n\n### `vue_alertes`\n\nUse for:\n\n- critical points\n- alerts\n- anomalies\n- exceptions\n- operational risk\n\n### `vue_resume_jour`\n\nUse for:\n\n- manager summary\n- transport recap\n- daily synthesis\n- what matters today\n\n## Routing Rule\n\nWhen a user asks a transport question:\n\n1. Detect the question family first.\n2. Call the matching tool before answering.\n3. Summarize the result naturally.\n4. Never answer from memory if a matching tool exists.\n\nIf several tools could apply, pick the one that answers the user's real intent most directly.\n\n## SQL Tool\n\nUse `execute_sql` only when you need direct database work that is not covered by a transport view.\n\n### Pattern\n\n- Read-only SQL can run directly.\n- Mutating SQL must be previewed first with `confirm=false`.\n- After explicit confirmation, run the same SQL again with `confirm=true`.\n- If `affectedRows = 0`, report that nothing changed.\n\n### Example\n\n```powershell\nmcporter call lumicore.execute_sql sql=\"SELECT 1;\" confirm=false\nmcporter call lumicore.execute_sql sql=\"UPDATE shipments SET zcontrat_0='embalage' WHERE zcontrat_0='COMFRAIS-EMB';\" confirm=false\nmcporter call lumicore.execute_sql sql=\"UPDATE shipments SET zcontrat_0='embalage' WHERE zcontrat_0='COMFRAIS-EMB';\" confirm=true\n```\n\n## Notes\n\n- Keep this file for transport-specific details only.\n- Use the workspace files and database-backed tools instead of guessing.\n- If a question sounds like a ranking, KPI, delay, alert, trend, or manager summary, call a tool first.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776949847276}}
